videos.headline: Air Force's miscommunication results in a Colorado State TD
videos.description: Air Force players collide in the backfield and Colorado State's Mohamed Kamara picks the ball up and goes 63 yards for the scoop-and-score touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Air Force's miscommunication results in a Colorado State TD) 2019/11/16

videos.headline: Air Force caps off win with 99-yard pick-six
videos.description: Colorado State looks like it will trim Air Force's lead, but Zane Lewis jumps the pass and goes 99 yards for a Falcons touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Air Force caps off win with 99-yard pick-6) 2019/11/16
